			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Go the Grove in WLD_Main_A (206; 25; 555)\r\n\"roll horrible\" in recon. Attack Guex (near the training the tiefling kids). Then attack him again during combat. He will say this AD regularly when you attck him during the combat."
				},
